                    <span id="c-1179864027" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1179864027" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1179864027">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/70085873/">若愚</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">做人之智慧，如果真能读透这本书绝对是人中之杰。只是大概读了一遍就对很多事物有全新看法。随着年龄增加多看多理解，绝对有助立足于社会。希望人生在世能悟透素书。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1156227534">
