    <div class="main review-item" id="4970509">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4970509/" class="title-link">素书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4970509"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/33035995/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u33035995-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/33035995/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">沟狗苟够</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-05-30"
      class="main-meta">2011-05-30 20:12:17</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4970509_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  修身、齐家、治国、平天下，步子大了容易扯着蛋。从基础做起，认识剖析自己。做人很简单，如何做好一个人却变成“绝非易事”。短短千余字助张良名扬天下，文不在冗长，鞭辟入里，如厕都可通读全文。言语简单，意欲深远。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4970509/#comments">(2回应)</a>
